metadata.name: RelatioNFT
metadata.description: RelatioNFT (RNFT) is a P2E NFT game about love, freedom of choice and acceptance across the whole Web3 community. 6,969 unique loving characters, created by our soft and caring hands, live, build relations and enjoy their lives on RNFT metaverse. RNFT is uniting artists, NFT enthusiasts and just ordinary loving people from around the globe.
